            "SummaryExplanation": {
                "val": "The program increase supports the workforce requirements necessary to support, manage, and  rapidly field technology to the fleet. The increase ensures funding is available to meet the salary needs of the current Scientific Program Officers workforce, the associated staff required to support the execution of the research, and an additional 20 FTE as determined by the recent ONR workforce shaping. FY21 increase supports CIVPER 1.9% pay raise.  \n\nTechnical: Not applicable."
